<strong>Metal-framed pack ladder</strong>

Vanilla sturdy backpack: 8 slots. This mod extends the ladder past steel.

<strong>Slots by tier</strong>
Mithril 10 / Adamantite 12 / Runite 14 / Dragon 16.

<strong>Recipes</strong>
Strictly sequential upgrade: previous bag at grid centre, plate above, rod below, sturdy leather at sides.

<strong>Look</strong>
Buckles textured per <a href="metals">metal</a>; rides the vanilla sturdy-backpack shape.
